## Import


Existing CIDR reservations can be imported using `SUBNET_ID:RESERVATION_ID`, e.g.,

```sh
 $ pulumi import aws:ec2/subnetCidrReservation:SubnetCidrReservation example subnet-01llsxvsxabqiymcz:scr-4mnvz6wb7otksjcs9
```
